strings:
<voice_0x01000FF8><se_def>Dhoulmagus: Well, well!
What persistent fools, coming after me in here!
<voice_0x01000FF9><se_def>Dhoulmagus: If I'm not mistaken, you're the very same servants of Trode I had the displeasure of meeting at Maella Abbey.
<voice_0x01000FFA><se_def>Dhoulmagus: So! You think you can defeat me and lift your master's curse!

<voice_0x01000FFB><se_def>Dhoulmagus: Ha ha ha! What admirable loyalty!
But alas, I am not receiving visitors at present!

<voice_0x01000FFC><se_def>Dhoulmagus: I'm healing. This magic is so overwhelming
that my body can hardly contain it.
Such is its power!
<voice_0x01000FFD><se_def>Dhoulmagus: A small price to pay for obtaining such unimaginable might!
<voice_0x01000FFE><se_def>Dhoulmagus: Anyway, you won't be staying long, will you!?
<voice_0x01001000><se_def>Dhoulmagus: You won't be able to fulfil your master's wish.
<voice_0x01001001><se_def>Dhoulmagus: But at least you shall fulfil your own destiny. To die at my hand!

<voice_0x01001002><se_def>Dhoulmagus: Tut, tut! We never learn, do we!?
You've come back for more?
<voice_0x01001003><se_def>Dhoulmagus: One wishes to turn his master back to normal. Another wishes to avenge her brother's death... I see you all have your own pitiful circumstances.

<voice_0x01001004><se_def>Dhoulmagus: But the most pitiful thing of all is this!
You will never defeat me, no matter how many times you try!
<voice_0x01001005><se_def>Dhoulmagus: Did you really imagine you could stand up to one as mighty as I? Your fates are sealed, worthless fools!
